                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180909-317-off1743 t18180909-317-crimeloc1745"></join>. On the 8th of September, between six and seven o'clock at night, the prisoner came and said a person wanted my daughter, who does not live at home. I told him where to find her. I turned my back to go to the drawers while the prisoner was there. Soon after he was gone I missed the watch off the mantle-piece.</p>
               <p>
            
